### LESSON 7 — Connection Logic — IF YEH KARO TU KYA HOGA

#### SCENARIO 1: theme.liquid mein change karo
```
IF: theme.liquid mein kuch change kiya
THEN: Har page pe change dikhai dega
WHY: Kyunki har page theme.liquid se guzarta hai

Example: theme.liquid mein font load kiya
Result: Poori website pe font change ho gaya
```

#### SCENARIO 2: Section file delete karo
```
IF: sections/header.liquid delete kiya
THEN: Har page pe header missing ho jayega
WHY: theme.liquid header section ko call karta hai

Error: "Could not find asset sections/header.liquid"
```

#### SCENARIO 3: settings_schema.json mein galti
```
IF: settings_schema.json mein range step galat
THEN: Theme customizer mein error aayega
WHY: Shopify schema validate karta hai load pe

Error: "Setting 'bar_height' must be a step in the range"
```

#### SCENARIO 4: Snippet rename karo
```
IF: snippets/price.liquid ko snippets/my-price.liquid kiya
THEN: Har jagah price nahi dikhega jahan render tha
WHY: {% render 'price' %} → file dhundhti hai 'price' naam se

Error: "Could not find asset snippets/price.liquid"
```

#### SCENARIO 5: assets mein JS add karo
```
IF: assets/my-feature.js banaya but load nahi kiya
THEN: Feature kaam nahi karega
WHY: File exist karti hai but koi load nahi kar raha

Fix: Section ya theme.liquid mein script tag add karo
```

