### LESSON 10 — Common Mistakes Aur Unka Logic

```
MISTAKE 1: Same ID do sections mein
PROBLEM:   Shopify confuse ho jata hai
FIX:       Har section ke IDs mein unique prefix lagao

MISTAKE 2: External CSS file jo exist nahi
PROBLEM:   404 error — style load nahi hoti
FIX:       CSS section file mein hi likho

MISTAKE 3: JavaScript global scope mein
PROBLEM:   Doosre sections ke JS se conflict
FIX:       Hamesha IIFE use karo

MISTAKE 4: Range step galat
PROBLEM:   Customizer error — setting save nahi hoti
FIX:       (max-min)/step <= 100 formula check karo

MISTAKE 5: block.shopify_attributes missing
PROBLEM:   Editor mein block highlight nahi hota
FIX:       Har block div pe {{ block.shopify_attributes }}

MISTAKE 6: Snippet naam galat
PROBLEM:   Render error — page crash
FIX:       {% render 'exact-file-name' %} — extension nahi
```

