Section Ka Structure (Har Section Mein):
{% comment %} HTML + Liquid Logic {% endcomment %}
<div class="section-hero">
  {% for block in section.blocks %}
    {{ block content }}
  {% endfor %}
</div>

{% comment %} CSS (scoped to this section) {% endcomment %}
<style>
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} { ... }
</style>

{% comment %} JavaScript (if needed) {% endcomment %}
<script src="{{ 'hero.js' | asset_url }}" type="module"></script>

{% comment %} Schema (settings for Customizer) {% endcomment %}
{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Hero Banner",
  "settings": [ ... ],
  "blocks": [ ... ]
}
{% endschema %}
WHY Sections zaroori hain?
Modular design — ek feature = ek section
Customizable — merchant settings se design change kare
Reusable — ek section multiple pages pe use ho
Independent — ek section ka code doosri pe affect nahi karta
IF section file mein kuch karo THEN:
Section ka naam change karo schema mein → Customizer mein naya naam dikhega
Section delete karo → Woh section use karne wale templates crash karenge
Schema mein naya setting add karo → Customizer mein naya option dikhega
