📁 FOLDER 7: config/ — SETTINGS SYSTEM
Kya hai?
Yeh Shopify ka Theme Customizer system hai. Merchant in settings se poori theme control karta hai.

Files:
File	Role
settings_schema.json	Schema — "kya options available hain?"
settings_data.json	Data — "merchant ne kya choose kiya?"
settings_schema.json ka Structure:
[
  {
    "name": "theme_info",           ← Theme ki info
    "theme_name": "Horizon",
    "theme_version": "3.5.1",
    "theme_author": "Shopify"
  },
  {
    "name": "Logo and Favicon",     ← Logo settings section
    "settings": [
      { "type": "image_picker", "id": "logo" },
      { "type": "range", "id": "logo_height", "min": 12, "max": 100 }
    ]
  },
  {
    "name": "Colors",               ← Color schemes
    "settings": [
      { "type": "color_scheme_group", "id": "color_schemes" }
    ]
  }
  // ... Typography, Layout, Cart, Social, etc.
]
WHY Config important hai?
Without schema → Customizer mein koi option nahi dikhega
Without data → Merchant ki saved settings lost ho jayengi
Schema galat → Customizer crash karega
IF config mein kuch karo THEN:
settings_schema.json mein naya setting add karo → Customizer mein naya option aayega
settings_data.json delete karo → Merchant ki saari saved settings reset ho jayengi
Range step galat diya → Error: "Setting must be a step in the range"
